WEBVTT

00:06.234 --> 00:08.397
Maybe it's not where an athlete is from...

00:11.255 --> 00:12.885
...that makes us root for them.

00:15.713 --> 00:18.061
Maybe it's not the flag on their back...

00:20.791 --> 00:23.697
...or the anthem that we hear when they win...

00:26.174 --> 00:27.409
...that makes us cheer.

00:30.567 --> 00:31.615
Maybe it's simply...

00:34.335 --> 00:35.283
...that they are human.

00:38.229 --> 00:39.857
And we are human.

00:42.438 --> 00:44.337
And when they succeed,...

00:47.289 --> 00:48.785
...we succeed.

00:53.945 --> 00:59.573
Visa, proud sponsor of the Olympic Games and the only card accepted there.

